{
    "chapter": 95,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "95:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以无花果及长无花果树木的地方盟誓，以橄榄及长橄榄树的地方盟誓，那便是真主派遣先知尔萨（愿主赐其平安）之地-巴勒斯坦。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "95:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以祂的先知穆萨（愿主赐其平安）获救的西奈山盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "95:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以禁寺之地-麦加盟誓，那里进入者均得平安，是穆罕默德（愿主福安之）为圣的地方。</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "95:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确为人类创造了最正直的品德和最优美的形态。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "95:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后我使他们在今世逐渐走向衰老和昏聩，他们再无法像以前那样受益于自己的身体。犹如一个人，其天性向恶，就无益于他，那他必入火狱。</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "95:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>除信真主且行善的人，他们在死后将享有永不罄尽的赏赐，即乐园，那是因为他们熏陶了自己的性情。</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "95:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！是什么使你们在眼见诸多证明真主大能的标志之后仍否认清算之日呢？</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "95:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类啊！难道真主没有使复活日成为最公正和最智慧的报酬的日子吗？难道真主会放任祂的众仆，对他们毫不判决，并以善果奖赏行善者，以恶果惩罚作恶者吗？</p>"
        }
    }
}